description:
This is a 21 minute workout called 'Targeted Upper + Lower Body Circuit ' from the channel Rina Thomas.
The workout falls under Strength/Calisthenics.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Weights and Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Rhythmic Powerhouse and The Warrior Workout vibe.
The The Rhythmic Powerhouse vibe means Beat-driven, strong but fluid, music-infused. This is especially good for When you want strength and rhythm to blend seamlessly. The The Warrior Workout vibe means Unleash your inner beast. Sweat-dripping, heart-pounding, primal energy. This is especially good for Days when you want to destroy stress and feel invincible..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Total body work with dumbbells off Hydrow and short intervals on Hydrow. Explicit lyrics. 

Max rhythm: 26, Format: EMOM...
